
AutoCurriculum RL Engine — Reinforcement Learning for Math Curricula

AutoCurriculum RL Engine is a self‑learning system that designs personalized math curricula using reinforcement learning. It dynamically selects exercise types and difficulty levels, evaluates student responses, and refines its policy to maximize accuracy, speed, and long‑term mastery.

