🧩 Extended Description
AutoCurriculum RL Engine is an advanced educational AI system that applies reinforcement learning to optimize math curricula. By modeling student performance as a dynamic environment, the agent selects exercises across multiple domains, adjusting difficulty and problem type to maximize learning efficiency. Each student response generates a reward signal reflecting accuracy, speed, and error reduction, enabling the agent to refine its policy and discover optimal learning paths. Unlike static adaptive systems, AutoCurriculum evolves curricula through experimentation, analytics, and continuous feedback, making it a powerful tool for intelligent tutoring, automated assessment, and AI‑driven education research.

